oai_dc:dc.dc:title: McCampbell barn
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Barn of Edward A. McCampbell, McCampbell Road, Knox County, TN. About 1902. Barn was blown down by a tornado on March 25, 1935. Shows men, children, horses, wood.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: barns, horses
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Knox County Two Centuries Photograph Project
